{"tid":1496660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被影大頭相送中（附聊天紀錄），來港參與反送中遊行中國朋友返回中國後在家被捕","createTime":"2019-08-22T15:31:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T15:54:46.000Z","uid":294761,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"50554a217e91f5681b08cbc8b9f792ef902eb92d","tid":1496660,"uid":294761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T15:31:53.000Z","msg":"朋友一向關心香港狀況，上兩個禮拜來港參與反送中遊行，過程也頗小心，為免被誤會係鬼，電話wallpaper係I love Taiwan, 遊行期間大部分時間都有戴口罩，番中國前都有delete曬所有聊天記錄同相片，點知道佢女朋友搵唔到佢於是搵我問，後來先知到佢係屋企被人拉左，原因係有佢係遊行現場嘅相，好彩佢屋企人幫佢搵律師，拘留二十四個鐘先放左，期間冇嘢食，唔比訓。冇搵律師嘅話可能要坐三年以上。<br />\n我而家都好驚，因為我隔一排都要去中國，但係我好多時發夢都會冇戴口罩，睇來真係要用新電話去中國，入面都要加啲我愛中國啲膠嘢，總之，大家冇咩必要真係唔好去中國！<br />\nanyway，聽日都會去手牽手，香港加油！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Dt4bTE4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDt4bTE4.jpg&h=4d0cc55f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/81020j5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F81020j5.jpg&h=1f62ca32&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HZDLX6L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHZDLX6L.jpg&h=7266a3a9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aR2T6Z6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaR2T6Z6.jpg&h=dcfc3ded&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3w9n0j6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3w9n0j6.jpg&h=2cb0cd38&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CXPbTE7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCXPbTE7.jpg&h=a4decd05&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c9MNrZ7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc9MNrZ7.jpg&h=95d4b933&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4d477490972d63943ee81a83445fd7d5197d11c9","tid":1496660,"uid":63909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-22T15:33:48.000Z","msg":"點會唔知we7會被監視..."},{"pid":"5883c9555dee96b323a1f5d09